ProMED-mail from HealthMap Alerts
<promed@promedmail.org>

[Ukraine should consider making vaccination mandatory except for medical reasons, e.g., immunocompromised conditions, especially during outbreaks of measles. The report states that the number of cases/deaths recorded are not at the level where an outbreak would be declared.

